s account, the cultural meanings of modernity}{\cs17\fs24\super 1{\footnote\ftnalt \pard\plain \s16\ql \li0\ri0\sl480\slmult1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
