y need to include the double consciousness of temporalities, since it absorbs, from within and outside Western rhetoric, the language of enlightenment rationality and democratic traditions of free expression (48).  The expectation that gendered expression
s of black Atlanticism might necessarily express a stylistic break with the canons of 19}{\fs24\super th}{\fs24 
 century poetic expressions then, may be as narrow as the old expectation that modern blank Atlanticism, is cut off from traditions of international modernist experimentation as a primary source of inspiration and ambition.
